title: Boosting Uruguay’s Economy: How Reforms and Artificial Intelligence Could Transform Growth
description: An IMF–World Bank study says Uruguay can accelerate growth by pairing long-delayed structural reforms with artificial intelligence adoption, boosting productivity, investment, and innovation.
